SMAFormulaTitle = Einfacher gleitender Durchschnitt
SMAFormulaDesc = SMA = Sum of last %s Monate demand / %s. Equal weight to all periods.
WMAFormulaTitle = Gewichteter gleitender Durchschnitt
WMAFormulaDesc = WMA = Sum(qty x weight) / Sum(weights). Recent Monate weighted more heavily (e.g. 3-month: weights 3,2,1).
SeasonalFormulaTitle = Saisonindex
SeasonalFormulaDesc = Saisonindex = Monat Average / Overall Monatly Average. Index > 1 means above-average demand for that month.
MAPEFormulaDesc = MAPE = mittlerer absoluter prozentualer Fehler = (1/n) x Summe(|Ist - Prognose| / Ist) x 100. Niedriger ist besser.
